{"tid":296253,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企隻貓嘔極都嘔唔出","createTime":"2017-06-24T12:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T15:24:34.000Z","uid":64628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"168c428fd6cfd437320e121e86b37724fc36fe51","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"我隻喵女兩歲半 除左bb個陣試過腸胃炎 之後都無病過<br />\n跟住兩日前佢無啦啦叫聲尖左勁多 隔多陣仲叫唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻望下主人點啦 佢有食野有飲水 屙屎都正常<br />\n上網睇完 話可能卡左毛係胃 咁我尋日買完化毛膏就餵佢食<br />\n餵完一兩個鐘後佢就作嘔啦 見佢自己係咁chok個身 但chok極都無野嘔出黎 一陣就停左<br />\n然後今朝未訓醒又聽到佢作嘔 但又見唔到嘔吐物<br />\n跟住直到岩岩屋企人又話佢作嘔<br />\n想問下咁樣會唔會有咩大問題 定點<br />\n最驚佢食左咩橡筋之類既野"},{"pid":"906b6242371289c400e91f9e77a625e0655e4f0b","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:09:38.000Z","msg":"佢細個病 我餵完佢食藥 佢苦到洗眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚再見到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果兩日內都係咁 一定捉佢去睇醫生"},{"pid":"f007372e6ca8874ecd28a1faaa61034fdc848f91","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"65b5111b21fbe9ce5fcaaa1d655ece7396a84213","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"0257a8c055ab55d8ce51533beed28b98fe0fa07e","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"陣間番屋企先睇到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de66e4e21f7ba7dff43b897a0a3baa1bec60d23","tid":296253,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"